{"tid":553300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【平昌冬奧】贊助商三星派4000手機 北韓伊朗選手無份","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T13:39:53.000Z","uid":73262,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"495737d967fad530aef77252986266b1ba697889","tid":553300,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"南韓平昌冬季奧運會本周五揭幕，冬奧贊助商三星電子會向所有選手和國際奧委會（IOC）工作人員免費送出「奧運版」Galaxy Note 8，不過由於擔心會違反聯合國制裁，北韓和伊朗選手都無份。<br />\n三星電子送出的4,000部「奧運版」Galaxy Note 8，每部零售價為100萬韓圜（約7,400港元），但22名北韓及4名伊朗選手就不能獲得手機，「因為聯合國的制裁，北韓和伊朗運動員會被排除在外」。<br />\n根據聯合國制裁，各國禁止向北韓和伊朗提供奢侈品，因擔心會被用於軍事方面發展。<br />\n另外美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）表示，華府不會容許北韓「騎劫」平昌冬奧，「我們不會讓北韓的宣傳騎劫奧運會所帶出的信息和形象。」他又稱美國很快會提出「歷來最嚴厲」的針對北韓經濟制裁，直至北韓同意解決核問題為止。<br />\n韓聯社/法新社/德新社<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180207&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57803342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180207%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57803342&d=0NtIp6AWbsTciRjD%2FUosWEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=23ffb25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180207%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57803342&h=83efcad6\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180207&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57803342</a>"},{"pid":"f5b13bb5ef98bba55873aac3b7fbcae563081a82","tid":553300,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1258707c468bce0307d7b6e0c1b5cac1ab8b1e6","tid":553300,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"炸彈？定裝咗間諜軟件？"},{"pid":"d650508e19f9acc8cff4cef0de4809e082b77922","tid":553300,"uid":76728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1258707c468bce0307d7b6e0c1b5c